result.title: Hi, Aman!
result.content:
Hi Aman,

How are you? Every week here will be posted different problems. There would be must-know problems, classic problems, problems that require algorithms, etc. Overall the material would be dedicated to increase your knowledge in Algorithms and Data Structures, and to ace the high rating in competitive programming. So you should do your best to succeed in this type of practice. Try to visit this group page as often as possible. That's all for now! Good luck in your new beginnings!

Your loving brother,
Pernekhan Utemuratov
